Package: webretrieveR
Type: Package
Title: Live Web Retrieval for R with LLM Context Injection
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lazaro", "Alvarez", 
           email = "lazarusalvarez3@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides an R-first interface to search the live web (via Tavily, 
    DuckDuckGo Instant Answer, etc.), fetch and clean pages, and inject 
    the results into Large Language Model chat clients (e.g. via 'ellmer'). 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
